### Arabic

[…](ayah-20) طَاعَةٌ وَقَوْلٌ مَّعْرُوفٌ ۚ فَإِذَا عَزَمَ ٱلْأَمْرُ فَلَوْ صَدَقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ لَكَانَ خَيْرًا لَّهُمْ

### English

[…](ayah-20) to obey and speak rightly. Then when fighting was ordained, it surely would have been better for them if they were true to Allah.